name: Tim Hammer
bio:
Young, fresh, full of life and Totino's pizza, Tim Hammer's style revolves around one-liners. Audience members often share his one-liners with their friends, and possibly enemies.

In 2013, Tim performed at Bridgetown Comedy Festival, was a finalist in the Portland's Funniest Person Contest, and then a finalist in the Big Sky International Comedy Competition. He has performed at venues such as the Hollywood Improv, Helium Comedy Club, Seattle Comedy Underground, and Applebee's.

In 2014, he performed at a Denny's.

He does not lip-sync any of his material.
